replyTime":"2019-04-05T07:54:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:06:45.000Z","msg":"咁都叫食碗面反碗底？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw lm 等滴滴殺落來 斬殺班車主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c434400f96c05481fc9d01d884377432a0d8a821","tid":1092828,"uid":17103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T09:54:39.000Z","msg":"因為有 D 撚樣話趕時間無得唔搭的士, 的士狗坐撚大怕你平民有牙.<br />\n間車行有心就賣撚晒 d 的士再買私家車做 Uber 車行，一樣咁租比人洗撚的士? 到個個人都唔洗要的士搵食時呢個大米倉自然會瓦解."},{"pid":"06793d2e803f58b6ed5dad4fed7f7273eda5aa4e","tid":1092828,"uid":160269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"自由市場 我繼續選擇uber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8598f0043788369908131e427508f00fadc3d5d","tid":1092828,"uid":20035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"因為本身的士個保險貴過普通第三保好多<br />\n個個做Uber就冇左舊生意"},{"pid":"f26c325bb0360262c9986dfa6a4641d0e931d352","tid":1092828,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8598f0043788369908131e427508f00fadc3d5d","tid":1092828,"uid":20035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:09:40.000Z","msg":"因為本身的士個保險貴過普通第三保好多<br />\n個個做Uber就冇左舊生意"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T10:14:04.000Z","msg":"普遍的士司機都過50歲，風險高，保費高"},{"pid":"0e674e11b034c66593f72dff0eb678856bb6065b","tid":1092828,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:12:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cf4ba18cb54af678bc5ef8c52e482c370e3a3327","tid":1092828,"uid":39552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"3697b0c3bb2834ff624a3dbcb35a3a2d849c9596","tid":1092828,"uid":67212,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T17:23:30.000Z","msg":"其實佢得20部 唔講出黎都無人知佢做u er啦<br />\n開得名都on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clo